      "settings": {
        "main": true,
        "title": "FurGIV - Pawful of Chalk",
        "meta_descr": "FurGIV (Furry Gathering In Vietnam) is a Vietnamese furry event for all furries in the country to meet one another, and to welcome international friends to our home country.\n\nOur mission is to create a safe space and environment for all furries to be able to express themselves while learning about the Vietnamese culture.",
