          "_name": "article02",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"start article2\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"8\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"8\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/furgiv-logo-final-1.svg\">\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t<header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\n\t<div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/furgiv20202620goh-1036x544.png\" alt=\"GOH Art\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Guest of Honor</b></h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Chucky</b></h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n\t\t\t\t\tClass, please meet the fantastical, magical freelance artist… Chucky!<br><br>Chucky here is a freelance artist who specializes in comics and webtoons. Principal Lam even heard that their specialty is all sorts of medieval fantasy topics, ranging from mundane slice-of-life to grand adventures. In fact, they are hoping that they can create an original series about humans, furries, and fantastical creatures living together in the future.<br><br>Needless to say, Principal Lam and the FurGIV School Board are very much looking forward to what they will bring to the class of FurGIV 2026!<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" href=\" https://chuckycomm.carrd.co/\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-globe-2 mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span></a>\n          <a class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chubberwocky/\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><span class=\"socicon socicon-facebook mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span></a>\n          <a class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" href=\"https://x.com/chubberwocky\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><span class=\"socicon socicon-twitter mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span></a></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div></section>",
